{"tid":1395120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3人涉藏爆炸品被捕　警方稱警署外放煙花案是調查方向","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:26:24.000Z","uid":274336,"like":1,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"357ee8b23f22c1673488d59da7a28f805c7518ce","tid":1395120,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"警方在天水圍天瑞邨一個單位，搜出一批自製的煙霧彈，拘捕單位內兩女一男，涉嫌無牌藏有爆炸品。<br />\n<br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科警司楊耀宗表示，下午近5時根據線報搜查單位，找到30枚煙霧彈、半製成品、硝酸鉀等原材料和工具。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士分別是母親和她的一子一女，年齡介乎23至47歲，要進一步調查誰人藏有煙霧彈，以及和最近示威遊行是否有關，又說早前天水圍警署外有人向人群放煙花的案件，是其中一個調查方向。至於煙霧彈的威力，楊耀宗說要由爆炸品處理課進一步調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471990-20190801.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471990-20190801.htm&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=02363958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471990-20190801.htm&h=de3bec6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471990-20190801.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n我無嘢講，我只係將分享新聞內容"},{"pid":"bc9f7c4516787d26acd206ef4cf8aab5b9dcb418","tid":1395120,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759917cb07430164707b3dd6543622996326cb72","tid":1395120,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"天水圍係咪要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ad2959ab534f69fd56bd53b3f922607e3256bc","tid":1395120,"uid":84102,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"黑警又砌人生百豬肉"},{"pid":"3b41d74794a7b29384f2022491f4c1760a66894d","tid":139512